Hi,

`union {
  TReal values[3];
  struct {
    TReal x, y, z;
  };
};`

This code is not permitted for C++11, only for C.

We can introduce something like:

`union vector3 {
  TReal values[3];
  struct {
    TReal x, y, z;
  };
};`

See http://stackoverflow.com/questions/2253878/why-does-c-disallow-anonymous-structs-and-unions .

